The FUMA Experience
Located in the Midtown area in Tallahassee, Florida,
Fuma Cigar Social
is a
Premium Cigar Lounge
dedicated to cigar enthusiast and their guests. From our well stocked walk-in humidor to the state-of-the-art air filtration system that keeps the environment fresh and friendly, Fuma Cigar Social is
THE PLACE
to sit back, relax and enjoy a fine cigar, a beer, wine or the best Cuban coffee you’ve ever had!
You know… life’s simple pleasures.
Visit Us!
Open hours
Sunday:
3 – 10p
Monday – Wednesday:
3 – 11p

Come visit the premier lounge of Tallahassee!
It’s all about the connections. Come by and relax in comfort. You’ll love our friendly and knowledgeable staff.
More Photos
More Photos
Wine
Our wine selection is crafted by sommeliers to deliver a superb tasting experience for all levels of wine connoisseurs. For more discerning customers, we have a fine selection of reserve bottles. Please inquire with our hosts.
Beer
If you like meeting great people, come to the bar! We support some of your favorite local breweries and have a wide variety to find you some new favorites.
View  Beer and Wine
Fall in love with our made-fresh
Cuban Coffee!
Delicious Dulce de Leche
Available with caramel.
Did someone say
Hookah?
Premium shisha in multiple flavors.
This month’s highlight
We Recommend…
Check out our cigar and beer of the month. We also have some great suggestions if you’re trying to find the perfect pairing.
Cigar of the Month
Oliva Serie V 135th Anniversary
Oliva Serie V ranks among the top cigars on the market year after year. With this special release, Oliva pays tribute to the year 1886 – it was 135 years ago when
Melanio Oliva
got his start working in the tobacco fields in Cuba. And what better way to honor this family patriarch than with a new Limited-Edition size of the beloved Serie V blend.
-.cigarsinternational.com
Beer of the Month
Victory Sour Monkey
Fruity notes from imported Belgian yeast swirl through a precise souring. Pucker up to a bite of citrus laden tang ending with a delectable experience.
-beeradvocate.com
⇔
Undercrown 10
+
Left Hand Peanut Butter Milk Stout
Try these TOGETHER!
Delirium Red
+
Isla Del Sol
⇔

Yelp Review
Fuma is one of my favorite places in Tallahassee. The vibe is chill and the ambiance is so relaxing.

Yelp Review
Top notch. High class. Superior service. Great selection.
Ryan B.
Yelp Review
Beautiful cigar lounge, great background music and of course a nice selection of cigars.

Yelp Review
Great for dates or groups. Also large beer and wine selection.

Yelp Review

Yelp Review
